book-text-doodle-rift-guide = Greetings, agent. You are likely wondering why the rift is contained in a flatpack.
      You see, that part isn't important- what is, however, is how to safely utilize this technology.

      - First, enter a secluded area such as Maintenance.
      - Then, unpack the provided flatpack with your given Multitool.
      - The rift will begin to "Charge" for around 30 seconds, before stabalizing.

      The rift will ocassionaly let out entities to attack the crew. They have no alligence, and will likely kill someone if they are unprepared.
      Good luck, agent.
